# direnv configuration — auto-loads infra/.env into the shell environment.
# Requires direnv: https://direnv.net
#
# Setup (one-time):
#   1. Install direnv and hook it into your shell (see docs/DEPLOYMENT_SUMMARY.md)
#   2. Copy infra/example.env -> infra/.env and fill in your values
#   3. Run: direnv allow
#
# After that, entering this directory auto-exports all TF_VAR_* variables,
# so `terraform plan/apply` picks them up without any manual sourcing.

dotenv infra/.env
